<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>INTERNAL — Freeze Letter Silence Alert {{ case_id }}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px;color:#111;line-height:1.5">

<div style="background:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #dc2626;padding:16px;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:24px">
  <p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#7f1d1d;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;font-weight:700">
    Internal Alert — Operator Action Required
  </p>
  <h2 style="margin:8px 0 0;font-size:18px">14-Day Issuer Silence on Freeze Request</h2>
</div>

<p>
  This is an automated internal alert. The freeze letter for case
  <strong>{{ case_id }}</strong> has now been silent for
  <strong>{{ days_since_sent }} days</strong> with no response from
  the issuer compliance team, despite two prior contacts:
</p>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;font-size:14px;margin:18px 0;background:#f9fafb;padding:12px;border-radius:4px">
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280;width:40%">Issuer</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0"><strong>{{ issuer }}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">Issuer contact</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0"><code style="font-size:12px">{{ contact_email or "(none recorded)" }}</code></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">Target wallet</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0;font-family:monospace">{{ target_address }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">Asset</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">{{ asset_symbol }}{% if chain %} on {{ chain }}{% endif %}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">Amount at risk</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0"><strong>USD {{ requested_freeze_usd_human }}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">Original letter sent</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">{{ sent_at_human }} UTC</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">72h nudge</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">sent — no response</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#6b7280">7d escalation</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">sent — no response</td></tr>
</table>

<h3 style="font-size:16px;margin-top:24px">Recommended next steps</h3>

<ol style="padding-left:24px">
  <li style="margin-bottom:10px">
    <strong>Pivot to a grand jury subpoena.</strong> Informal
    freeze requests have been exhausted. If you have a cooperating
    AUSA, generate a subpoena via:
    <pre style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px">recupero legal-request {{ case_id }} --type subpoena --target "{{ issuer }}"</pre>
  </li>
  {% if jurisdiction and jurisdiction != "US" %}
  <li style="margin-bottom:10px">
    <strong>{{ issuer }} is in {{ jurisdiction }} jurisdiction.</strong>
    Consider an MLAT request via DOJ-OIA:
    <pre style="background:#f3f4f6;padding:8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px">recupero legal-request {{ case_id }} --type mlat --target "{{ issuer }}"</pre>
  </li>
  {% endif %}
  <li style="margin-bottom:10px">
    <strong>Document the non-response timeline.</strong> The system
    has recorded a <code>silence_14d</code> outcome row for this
    letter, which will be surfaced in the LE handoff's
    "Filing Status" section and feed into the per-issuer priors
    refresh tonight.
  </li>
  <li style="margin-bottom:10px">
    <strong>Notify the victim.</strong> Their case update should be
    re-issued with the revised recoverable estimate (the priors
    section in the LE handoff has been recomputed accordingly).
  </li>
</ol>

<p style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;margin-top:24px">
  No further automated follow-ups will be sent to the issuer on
  this letter — the followup_stage has advanced to
  <code>silence_14d</code> (terminal). The 30-day and 90-day
  silence outcomes will continue to land if you record them via
  <code>recupero-ops record-freeze-outcome</code>.
</p>

<hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;margin:24px 0">

<p style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280">
  Auto-generated by Recupero freeze-followup cron.
  This message is intended for the case investigator
  ({{ investigator_email }}) — NOT for the issuer.
</p>

</body>
</html>
